//━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// PANEL (✅ FIX: versión actualizada a v3.5)
//━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
var table panel = na

if barstate.islast and showPanel
    if not na(panel)
        table.delete(panel)

    // ── Panel position & size helpers ──
    string pS = panelSize
    string pP = panelPos
    string pPos = pP == "Med. Derecha" ? position.middle_right :
                  pP == "Inf. Derecha" ? position.bottom_right  :
                  pP == "Inf. Centro"  ? position.bottom_center :
                  pP == "Centro"       ? position.middle_center :
                  position.top_right
    string pTxt  = pS == "Mediano" ? size.small  : pS == "Grande" ? size.normal : size.tiny
    string pTxtH = pS == "Mediano" ? size.normal : pS == "Grande" ? size.large  : size.small

    color bg = color.new(#0d1117, 0)
    float wr     = stat_total > 0 ? (stat_wins * 100.0 / stat_total) : 0.0
    color wrCol  = wr >= 50 ? #8FE28A : #ef5350
    float avgR   = stat_total > 0 ? stat_totalR / stat_total : 0.0
    string grade = avgR >= 2.0 ? "A+" : avgR >= 1.5 ? "A" : avgR >= 1.0 ? "B" : avgR >= 0.5 ? "C" : "D"
    color gradeCol = avgR >= 2.0 ? #8FE28A : avgR >= 1.5 ? #69F0AE : avgR >= 1.0 ? #FFD600 : avgR >= 0.5 ? #FF9800 : #ef5350
    string sessNow  = isAsia ? "Asia" : isLondon ? "London" : isNY ? "NY" : "Off"
    color mtfBull  = color.new(#26a69a, 0)
    color mtfBear  = color.new(#ef5350, 0)
    color mtfRevOn = color.new(#FFD600, 0)
    color mtfOff   = color.new(#30363d, 0)
    // Expectancy metrics
    float avgWinR   = stat_wins > 0 ? stat_winR / stat_wins : 0.0
    float avgLossR  = stat_losses > 0 ? stat_lossR / stat_losses : 0.0
    float expectR   = stat_total > 0 ? stat_totalR / stat_total : 0.0
    float payoff    = avgLossR > 0 ? avgWinR / avgLossR : 0.0
    float avgWinPct  = avgWinR * 100.0
    float avgLossPct = avgLossR * 100.0
    float expectPct  = expectR * 100.0
    color expectCol  = expectR >= 0 ? #8FE28A : #ef5350

    if active and not na(entryPrice)
        // ═══ PANEL EXPANDIDO — 16 filas ═══
        panel := table.new(pPos, 7, 16, bgcolor=bg, border_width=1, border_color=color.new(#30363d, 50), frame_width=1, frame_color=color.new(#30363d, 60))
        float pnl    = bull ? (close - entryPrice) / entryPrice * 100.0 : (entryPrice - close) / entryPrice * 100.0
        color pnlCol = pnl >= 0 ? #8FE28A : #ef5350
        color pnlBg  = color.new(pnl >= 0 ? #8FE28A : #ef5350, 90)
        int _tc = tradeConf
        string confTxt = _tc >= 5 ? "★★★★★" : _tc >= 4 ? "★★★★☆" : _tc >= 3 ? "★★★☆☆" : _tc >= 2 ? "★★☆☆☆" : "★☆☆☆☆"
        color  confCol = _tc >= 4 ? #8FE28A : _tc >= 3 ? #FFD600 : #FF9800
        color  secBg   = color.new(#161b22, 0)
        string dirTxt  = bull ? "▲  LONG" : "▼  SHORT"
        color  dirCol  = bull ? #8FE28A : #ef5350
        color  dirBg   = color.new(bull ? #8FE28A : #ef5350, 85)
        // ── Row 0 — Header con dirección del trade ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 0, "GAUSSIAN  v3.5", text_color=#8FE28A, text_size=pTxtH, bgcolor=secBg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 0, 4, 0)
        table.cell(panel, 5, 0, dirTxt, text_color=dirCol, text_size=pTxtH, bgcolor=dirBg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 5, 0, 6, 0)
        // ── Row 1 — Entrada ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 1, "ENTRADA", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 30), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 1, 2, 1)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 1, f_fmtPrice(entryPrice), text_color=#58A6FF, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_right)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 1, 6, 1)
        // ── Row 2 — Stop Loss ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 2, "STOP LOSS", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 30), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 2, 2, 2)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 2, f_fmtPrice(trailSL), text_color=#ef5350, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_right)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 2, 6, 2)
        // ── Row 3 — PnL (highlighted) ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 3, "PnL ACTUAL", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 30), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=pnlBg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 3, 2, 3)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 3, (pnl >= 0 ? "+" : "") + str.tostring(pnl, "#.##") + "%", text_color=pnlCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=pnlBg, text_halign=text.align_right)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 3, 6, 3)
        // ── Row 4 — WinRate + Confianza ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 4, "WR  " + str.tostring(wr, "#.#") + "%", text_color=wrCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left, tooltip="Winrate acumulado\n" + str.tostring(stat_wins) + "W  " + str.tostring(stat_losses) + "L  |  Avg " + str.tostring(avgR, "#.##") + "R")
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 4, 2, 4)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 4, confTxt + "  " + str.tostring(_tc) + "/5", text_color=confCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_right, tooltip="Confianza de la señal\nMás ★ = más filtros alineados")
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 4, 6, 4)
        // ── Row 5 — RENDIMIENTO separator ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 5, "  RENDIMIENTO", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=secBg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 5, 6, 5)
        // ── Row 6 — Gan Prom ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 6, "↑  Gan. Prom", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 6, 2, 6)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 6, "+" + str.tostring(avgWinPct, "#.##") + "%", text_color=#8FE28A, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=color.new(#8FE28A, 92), text_halign=text.align_right, tooltip="Ganancia promedio por trade ganador\n" + str.tostring(avgWinR, "#.##") + "R × " + str.tostring(stat_wins) + " wins")
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 6, 6, 6)
        // ── Row 7 — Pérd Prom ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 7, "↓  Pérd. Prom", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 7, 2, 7)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 7, "-" + str.tostring(avgLossPct, "#.##") + "%", text_color=#ef5350, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=color.new(#ef5350, 92), text_halign=text.align_right, tooltip="Pérdida promedio por trade perdedor\n" + str.tostring(avgLossR, "#.##") + "R × " + str.tostring(stat_losses) + " losses")
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 7, 6, 7)
        // ── Row 8 — Expectativa (highlighted) ──
        string expSign = expectPct >= 0 ? "+" : ""
        table.cell(panel, 0, 8, "✦  EXPECTATIVA", text_color=expectCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=color.new(expectR >= 0 ? #8FE28A : #ef5350, 90), text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 8, 2, 8)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 8, expSign + str.tostring(expectPct, "#.##") + "% / trade", text_color=expectCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=color.new(expectR >= 0 ? #8FE28A : #ef5350, 90), text_halign=text.align_right, tooltip="Ganancia esperada por trade\nSi es + → RENTABLE\nPayoff: " + str.tostring(payoff, "#.##") + ":1")
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 8, 6, 8)
        // ── Row 9 — TARGETS separator ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 9, "  TARGETS", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=secBg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 9, 6, 9)
        // ── Row 10 — TP Activo ──
        int tpOff = tp5_hit ? 5 : tp4_hit ? 4 : tp3_hit ? 3 : tp2_hit ? 2 : tp1_hit ? 1 : 0
        string n0 = tpOff == 0 ? "TP1" : tpOff == 1 ? "TP2" : tpOff == 2 ? "TP3" : tpOff == 3 ? "TP4" : tpOff == 4 ? "TP5" : "TP6"
        float  p0 = tpOff == 0 ? tp1P : tpOff == 1 ? tp2P : tpOff == 2 ? tp3P : tpOff == 3 ? tp4P : tpOff == 4 ? tp5P : tp6P
        table.cell(panel, 0, 10, "▶  " + n0 + "  ACTIVO", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 10, 2, 10)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 10, not na(p0) ? f_fmtPrice(p0) : "—", text_color=#58A6FF, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=color.new(#58A6FF, 92), text_halign=text.align_right)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 10, 6, 10)
        // ── Row 11 — TP Próximo ──
        string n1 = tpOff == 0 ? "TP2" : tpOff == 1 ? "TP3" : tpOff == 2 ? "TP4" : tpOff == 3 ? "TP5" : tpOff == 4 ? "TP6" : "TP7"
        float  p1 = tpOff == 0 ? tp2P : tpOff == 1 ? tp3P : tpOff == 2 ? tp4P : tpOff == 3 ? tp5P : tpOff == 4 ? tp6P : tp7P
        table.cell(panel, 0, 11, "○  " + n1 + "  PRÓXIMO", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 40), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 11, 2, 11)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 11, not na(p1) ? f_fmtPrice(p1) : "—", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_right)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 3, 11, 6, 11)
        // ── Row 12 — MTF separator + Sesión ──
        color sessCol12 = sessNow == "Off" ? color.new(#8b949e, 40) : color.white
        color sessBg12  = sessNow == "Asia" ? color.new(#9C27B0, 60) : sessNow == "London" ? color.new(#1565C0, 60) : sessNow == "NY" ? color.new(#00695C, 60) : color.new(#30363d, 60)
        table.cell(panel, 0, 12, "  MTF", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=secBg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 12, 4, 12)
        table.cell(panel, 5, 12, sessNow, text_color=sessCol12, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=sessBg12, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 5, 12, 6, 12)
        // ── Row 13 — Trend TF (arrows para dirección) ──
        table.cell(panel, 0, 13, "▲▼", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 40), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 1, 13, m5Bull  ? "5M ↑" : "5M ↓",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m5Bull  ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 2, 13, m15Bull ? "15M↑" : "15M↓", text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m15Bull ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 13, h1Bull  ? "1H ↑" : "1H ↓",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h1Bull  ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 4, 13, h4Bull  ? "4H ↑" : "4H ↓",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h4Bull  ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 5, 13, dBull   ? "1D ↑" : "1D ↓",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=dBull   ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 6, 13, "", bgcolor=bg)
        // ── Row 14 — Reversal TF (dn color when active) ──
        color mtfRevActive = color.new(dn, 0)
        table.cell(panel, 0, 14, "⚡", text_color=color.new(dn, 20), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 1, 14, "5M",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m5Rev  ? mtfRevActive : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 2, 14, "15M", text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m15Rev ? mtfRevActive : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 14, "1H",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h1Rev  ? mtfRevActive : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 4, 14, "4H",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h4Rev  ? mtfRevActive : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 5, 14, "1D",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=dRev   ? mtfRevActive : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 6, 14, "", bgcolor=bg)
        // ── Row 15 — Market Status bar ──
        color  mktBg  = isRanging ? color.new(#FF9800, 82) : color.new(#8FE28A, 90)
        string mktTxt = isRanging ? "⚠  LATERAL — señales bloqueadas" : "✓  TENDENCIA — sistema activo"
        color  mktCol = isRanging ? #FF9800 : #8FE28A
        table.cell(panel, 0, 15, mktTxt, text_color=mktCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=mktBg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 15, 6, 15)
    else
        // ═══ PANEL CONTRAÍDO — 6 filas ═══
        panel := table.new(pPos, 7, 6, bgcolor=bg, border_width=1, border_color=color.new(#30363d, 50), frame_width=1, frame_color=color.new(#30363d, 60))
        // Row 0 — Header
        table.cell(panel, 0, 0, "Gaussian Trend v3.5", text_color=#8FE28A, text_size=pTxtH, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 0, 6, 0)
        // Row 1 — WinRate
        table.cell(panel, 0, 1, grade, text_color=gradeCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center, tooltip="Performance: avg " + str.tostring(avgR, "#.##") + "x por cada 1 arriesgado")
        table.cell(panel, 1, 1, "WinRate", text_color=#8b949e, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.cell(panel, 2, 1, str.tostring(wr, "#.#") + "%  (" + str.tostring(stat_wins) + "/" + str.tostring(stat_total) + ")", text_color=wrCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_right)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 2, 1, 6, 1)
        // Row 2 — Expectancy
        string expSignC = expectPct >= 0 ? "+" : ""
        string ddStrC   = maxDrawdown > 0 ? "  DD " + str.tostring(maxDrawdown, "#.#") + "%" : ""
        table.cell(panel, 0, 2, expectR >= 0 ? "✦" : "✧", text_color=expectCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 1, 2, "Expectativa", text_color=#8b949e, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_left)
        table.cell(panel, 2, 2, expSignC + str.tostring(expectPct, "#.##") + "% / trade", text_color=expectCol, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=color.new(expectR >= 0 ? #8FE28A : #ef5350, 88), text_halign=text.align_right, tooltip=str.tostring(stat_wins) + "W  " + str.tostring(stat_losses) + "L" + ddStrC + "\nGan.Prom: +" + str.tostring(avgWinPct, "#.##") + "%  Pérd.Prom: -" + str.tostring(avgLossPct, "#.##") + "%\nPayoff: " + str.tostring(payoff, "#.##") + ":1")
        table.merge_cells(panel, 2, 2, 6, 2)
        // Row 3 — MTF separator
        table.cell(panel, 0, 3, "── MTF ──", text_color=color.new(#8b949e, 40), text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.merge_cells(panel, 0, 3, 6, 3)
        // Row 4 — Trend (equal-width cells)
        table.cell(panel, 0, 4, "T", text_color=#8b949e, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 1, 4, "5M",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m5Bull  ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 2, 4, "15M", text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m15Bull ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 4, "1H",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h1Bull  ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 4, 4, "4H",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h4Bull  ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 5, 4, "1D",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=dBull   ? mtfBull : mtfBear, text_halign=text.align_center)
        int revCountC = (m5Rev ? 1 : 0) + (m15Rev ? 1 : 0) + (h1Rev ? 1 : 0) + (h4Rev ? 1 : 0) + (dRev ? 1 : 0)
        color revBgC  = revCountC >= 3 ? color.new(#FFD600, 20) : revCountC >= 1 ? color.new(#FFD600, 60) : color.new(#30363d, 0)
        table.cell(panel, 6, 4, revCountC > 0 ? "⚡" + str.tostring(revCountC) : "—", text_color=revCountC > 0 ? #FFD600 : #8b949e, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=revBgC, text_halign=text.align_center, tooltip="Reversals activos\n5M:" + (m5Rev ? "✓" : "✗") + "  15M:" + (m15Rev ? "✓" : "✗") + "  1H:" + (h1Rev ? "✓" : "✗") + "  4H:" + (h4Rev ? "✓" : "✗") + "  1D:" + (dRev ? "✓" : "✗"))
        // Row 5 — Rev (equal-width cells)
        table.cell(panel, 0, 5, "R", text_color=#8b949e, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=bg, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 1, 5, "5M",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m5Rev  ? mtfRevOn : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 2, 5, "15M", text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=m15Rev ? mtfRevOn : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 3, 5, "1H",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h1Rev  ? mtfRevOn : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 4, 5, "4H",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=h4Rev  ? mtfRevOn : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 5, 5, "1D",  text_color=color.white, text_size=pTxt, bgcolor=dRev   ? mtfRevOn : mtfOff, text_halign=text.align_center)
        table.cell(panel, 6, 5, "", bgcolor=bg)
//━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
